{"tid":2070451,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"山西陽泉商業銀行擠提，副市長宣稱以「人格及黨性」為銀行作擔保","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T13:30:48.000Z","uid":48040,"like":123,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"8f80acefc2ee6eb6aa264e316b43f9d8269414a3","tid":2070451,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"近日，山西陽泉市商業銀行發生部分儲戶集中提取存款情況。6月17日，陽泉副市長黃海濤對聚集的當地民眾進行解釋稱陽泉商行目前運行正常，資金充沛，並願以市長身份、人格與黨性作擔保。<br />\n<br />\n6月18日，中國人民銀行陽泉市支行發佈公告：陽泉商行資金充裕，希望不信謠不傳謠。同日陽泉警方發布通報：已抓獲散佈銀行資金鍊斷裂謠言者，均被依法嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/402886382_114984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F402886382_114984&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=74f8f456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/402886382_114984</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1273870412758147074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273870412758147074&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=f0ee0f76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1273870412758147074&h=03467cdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1273870412758147074</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0iBFBs1MH3I&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=4e81ac0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I</a>"},{"pid":"18df26e99c60f637bc93b631aac3b67839f2e5e5","tid":2070451,"uid":56326,"like":264,"dislike":0,"score":264,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"第一次見有人用空氣做擔保"},{"pid":"368aed45d84779be37ff6e5b77b296f6739d928f","tid":2070451,"uid":151313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"咁仲死"},{"pid":"9570797651